  <section id="introduction">
    <section>
      Ways We Enjoy Magic Cards is a concise overview of Magic, a popular game that is addictive yet innocent.
    </section>
  
    <section>
      It lists dozens of ways to enjoy Magic's culture (many are free, most are affordable).  While explaining Magic's appeal, it shows how to join in.
    </section>
  </section>
  <%= wwemc_purchase "Let's play the game" %>
  <section id="license">
    <section>
      $2 gets you the book and sends it to (up to) four friends.  You'll all have lifetime access to our weekly updates.
    </section>
  
    <section>
      You'll receive a PDF and access to an online edition.  Since not everyone can make purchases online, we make a <%= link_to 'chapter', free_book_chapters_path(Book.featured) %> available for free every day.
    </section>
  </section>
  <%= wwemc_purchase "I have $2!" %>
