    <section>
      Magic: The Gathering was first played 25 years ago.  It rapidly spread, gradually developed, and after a couple big ups and downs, it has surged to a new peak.  There are millions of players in the US and millions more globally.
    </section>
  
    <section>
      Magic is not one game, but a framework for various formats, each of which creates different trends and challenges.  Ways We Enjoy Magic Cards will help you and your loved ones find formats that are fun for every occasion.
    </section>
  </section>
  <%= wwemc_purchase "That's worth more than $2" %>
</section>
